{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 that do deserve strict scrutiny, I argue that the dignitary interests of minority groups protected by 
}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_201202_644_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_201202_644_1}
{\b1 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
