{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EYVAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EYVAE_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
After confronting a history rife with racism, forced internment, and both governmental and private discrimination against racial and ethnic minorities, women, and the LGBT community, states and the federal governments have 
}
