{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 begun to pay more attention to the needs of minority groups. Governments trying to remedy the effects of systemic bigotry, which contributes to accumulated disadvantages and socio-cultural biases,
}
