{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0E6WAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0E6WAE_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In the commercial sector, business owners and employees have begun advancing compelled speech arguments against the application of laws designed to protect historically underprivileged groups.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
