{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0ELXAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0ELXAE_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Non-discrimination and public accommodations laws, originally enacted during the civil rights era, prevent discrimination on the basis of membership in particular groups, including on the basis of sexual orientation.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F26482421465_ID0ETXAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F26482421465_ID0ETXAE_1}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F26482421465_1" }{\fldrslt 
