{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0E5XAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0E5XAE_1}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Some religious people have claimed these laws compel their acceptance and participation in certain practices to which they have a moral objection. As examples, the Supreme Court recently decided 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i1 \fs20 
