28
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The Supreme Court did not address the compelled speech issue, leaving it open for future cases.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F29482421465_ID0EXYAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F29482421465_ID0EXYAE_1}
