{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In another context, states have authorized unions to require \u8220\'3ffair share fees,\u8221\'3f so that unions can perform their task of negotiating on behalf of employees.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F32482421465_ID0EH1AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F32482421465_ID0EH1AE_1}
