32
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 The history of unions is one of giving historically marginalized workers better protections and conditions against powerful employers.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F33482421465_ID0EM1AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F33482421465_ID0EM1AE_1}
