35
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Here, the proffered compelled speech exists in the form of compelled union dues used to support union activity. Even a non-union employee in states requiring fair share fees must contribute \u8220\'3fmoney for the propagation of opinions which he disbelieves.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F36482421465_ID0EJ2AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F36482421465_ID0EJ2AE_1}
