{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i1 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Lochner
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
,\u8221\'3f where business interests or political groups are using the First Amendment as a sword to advance their policy goals, instead of as a shield to simply protect their First Amendment rights against unconstitutional policy.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F37482421465_ID0EJ3AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F37482421465_ID0EJ3AE_1}
