37
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Power, not reason, is the Court\rquote s currency on these issues, some argue,
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F38482421465_ID0EM3AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F38482421465_ID0EM3AE_1}
