{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Further, in the clash of rights between religious objectors and members of historically persecuted communities, some argue to \u8220\'3fbeware of the false equivalence.\u8221\'3f
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F41482421465_ID0ET4AE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F41482421465_ID0ET4AE_1}
