{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 However, religious adherents may have mobilized as a political group because their First Amendment rights are being marginalized by the new, good orthodoxy. Further, the Court\rquote s dismantling economic regulation that affects speech has long been well intertwined with upholding First Amendment liberties, and, indeed, cannot be easily reduced to partisan lines.
}
