{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 This tension becomes apparent in the context of issues surrounding diversity measures to include members of historically underrepresented groups. The Supreme Court has held that public universities\rquote  academic freedom rights allow them to implement affirmative action plans that involve some racial discrimination against majority applicants in order to create diversity that enhances classroom discussion and the classroom experience.
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F52482421465_ID0E3FAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F52482421465_ID0E3FAG_1}
