{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Thus, despite the Equal Protection Clause of the Fourteenth Amendment, affirmative action may properly be employed to further the legitimate pedagogical goals of an institution.
}
