{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 As an extension of this, and to serve important pedagogical values, public universities often ask professors to demonstrate that they are fostering an environment that allows underrepresented minorities to feel welcome and included.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
