{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 Even more so, universities should not force professors to proclaim allegiance to a particular ideological, and perhaps partisan, view of how to foster diversity and inclusion, one that favors focusing on group membership, group benefits and penalties, and generalizations about how membership in particular groups affects our status, interactions, and opportunities.
