{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
The key to ensuring that individuals across the political spectrum can accept both the reasoning and the results in any given opinion will be drawing clear, meaningful, nonpartisan lines between speech and conduct that safeguard our ability to express unpopular sentiments while preserving laws that mainly target conduct and benefit groups who have been historically oppressed by our country\rquote s laws.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
